snippet.title: Sims 2 Castaway PSP on Android
snippet.description:
Sims 2 Castaway PSP on Android
Gameplay and Setting HD

My Gear :
Xiaomi Mi 5 Prime 3/64 2,15 GHz Adreno 530
PPSSPP (PSP Emulator) for android v1.4-2

SETTINGS
at 05:11

*Graphics
Backend : OpenGL
Mode : Buffered Rendering
Simulate block transfer effects : off/untick
Frameskipping : off
Rendering resolution : 3x PSP
Display resolution (HW scaler) : 3x PSP
Timer hack : on/tick

**Tools
Developer Tools
CPU Core : Dynarec (JIT) = Random Freeze = Monkey =
Solution = use Interpreter but very slow

***System
Multithreaded (experimental) : off/untick

Sims 2 Castaway Playable on Android
For complete tutorial step by step - How to Play PSP on Android Smartphone
Please check my video https://youtu.be/TWpLpNkbdYg

Please Comment, Like and Subscribe
Thank's
eDroid Gaming

Note :
This video for demo / educational purpose only
